        <mxCell id="Sw-CaN76OAAPuKDkVYWO-2" value="Organisational&amp;nbsp; structure&amp;nbsp; involves&amp;nbsp; arrangement&amp;nbsp; of&amp;nbsp; activities&amp;nbsp; and&amp;nbsp; assignment&amp;nbsp; of personnel to these activities in order to achieve the organisational goals in an efficient manner.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ineffective&amp;nbsp; strategy&amp;nbsp; /&amp;nbsp; structure&amp;nbsp; match&amp;nbsp; may&amp;nbsp; result&amp;nbsp; in&amp;nbsp; company&amp;nbsp; rigidity&amp;nbsp; and increases&amp;nbsp; the&amp;nbsp; complexity&amp;nbsp; and&amp;nbsp; need&amp;nbsp; for&amp;nbsp; rapid&amp;nbsp; changes&amp;nbsp; in&amp;nbsp; today’s&amp;nbsp; competitive landscape." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
