        <mxCell id="ObN9QLPdV3uD9SNAZ5Un-45" value="&lt;div&gt;• Creating separate divisions, each representing a distinct business&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;• Each division would house its functional hierarchy;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;• Division managers would be given responsibility for managing day-to-day&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;operations;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;• A small corporate office that would determine the long-term strategic direction of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;the firm and exercise overall financial control over the semi-autonomous divisions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1" visible="0">
