        <mxCell id="ObN9QLPdV3uD9SNAZ5Un-47" value="&lt;div&gt; It is a single business or collection of related businesses which offer scope for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;independent planning.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; Each SBU is different from other in the basic factors viz, mission, objectives and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;strategy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; Each SBU will have its own distinct set of competitors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; Each SBU will have a CEO who is responsible for strategic planning &amp;amp; profit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;performance of SBU.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; Each SBU is a separate business from the strategic planning standpoint. In the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;basic factors, viz., mission, objectives, competition and strategy-one SBU will be&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;distinct from another.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; Each SBU will have its own distinct set of competitors and its own distinct strategy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; Each SBU will have a CEO. He will be responsible for strategic planning for the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;SBU and its profit performance; he will also have control over most of the factors&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;affecting the profit of the SBU.&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1" visible="0">
          <mxGeometry x="263.75" y="1180" width="457.5" height="310" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ObN9QLPdV3uD9SNAZ5Un-50" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Advantages of SBU structure&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Delegation of authority and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;responsibility&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Ease in administration of large&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;number of divisions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Focus on co-ordination,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;communication and controls&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Individual SBUs are treated as&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;profit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- centers, they can react quickly to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;changes.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Promotes accountability&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Creates competitive environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;between divisions&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1" visible="0">
          <mxGeometry x="192.5" y="1530" width="280" height="350" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ObN9QLPdV3uD9SNAZ5Un-51" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Disadvantages of SBU structure&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Expensive on account of additional&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;layer.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Difficult to determine roles of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;different managers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- May result in inconsistency of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;goals&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Delay in decision making for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;significant decisions some times&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;because of various levels of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;management&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1" visible="0">
          <mxGeometry x="512.5" y="1530" width="280" height="230" as="geometry" />
