        <mxCell id="ObN9QLPdV3uD9SNAZ5Un-73" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;Network organisational structure primarily involved subcontracting some or all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;operating functions to other companies that are required to co-ordinate their&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;activities in consultation with the personnel at the headquarters of the networking&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;organisation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; The traditional functional areas of manufacturing quality control marketing and so&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;on are handled by different companies that are in constant touch with&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;headquarters where computers and telecommunications.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; Outsourcing the practice of taking a significant activity within the organisation and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;contracting it out to an independent party.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;The management outsources non vital&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;functions but retain strategic control.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;They find the best in class suppliers of goods&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;and services around the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;By avoiding large investment and fixed asset purchase&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;building plan equipment on the firms can increase their profit margins.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; It is a collection of independent firms linked through information systems that&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;produce or sell a product or service.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The firm&#39;s business functions will not be located in a single physical area, but will&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;be scattered. The head office will work as broker.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The firm is electronically&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;connected to some fully owned, or partly owned, or independent companies&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1" visible="0">
